# Copy this file to .github/CODEOWNERS and replace placeholders with real GitHub handles.
# Invalid CODEOWNERS entries may not enforce review, so do not use placeholders in a real repo.

.github/workflows/** @your-github-handle
.github/actions/** @your-github-handle
.github/CODEOWNERS @your-github-handle
deploy/** @your-github-handle
docs/ci/** @your-github-handle
docs/security/** @your-github-handle

# Agent harness ownership examples
AGENTS.md @your-github-handle
.agents/ @your-github-handle
docs/agent-rules/ @your-github-handle
docs/agent-manager/ @your-github-handle
